thread.title: BRIEF-Excelsior United Development Co Posts HY Group Pretax Profit Of 120.5 Mln Rupees

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Excelsior United Development Co Posts HY Group Pretax Profit Of 120.5 Mln Rupees

organizations.name: brief-excelsior united development co posts hy group pretax

text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Excelsior United Development Companies Ltd :
* FOR HY ENDED DEC 31, 2017, TURNOVER AT 338.7 MILLION RUPEES VERSUS 352.5 MILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO‍​
* HY GROUP PROFIT BEFORE TAX OF 120.5 MILLION RUPEES VERSUS 107.9 MILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO‍​ Source: bit.ly/2C6qqY1 Further company coverage: (Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
